"version": "1.0.4",
"title": "5973: unreliability",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5973",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The quality of a person or thing that cannot be trusted or relied upon. Scripture notes the unreliability of human nature, while stressing the total reliability of God.</p>\n<h2>Human nature is unreliable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:57\">PSA 78:57</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:15\">ISA 49:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:4\">HOS 6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:9\">2CO 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of unreliable people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:23\">GEN 40:23</a> <em>the chief cupbearer</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:13-1Sam13:14\">1SA 13:13–13:14</a> <em>King Saul</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:13\">HOS 5:13</a> <em>Israel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:40\">MAT 26:40</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:37\">MRK 14:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:45\">LUK 22:45</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:56\">MAT 26:56</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:50\">MRK 14:50</a></p>\n<h3>Unreliable people are not to be trusted</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:19\">PRO 25:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:3-Ps146:4\">PSA 146:3–146:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:22\">ISA 2:22</a></p>\n<h2>False gods are unreliable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:20\">ISA 45:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:28\">DEU 4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:4-Ps115:8\">PSA 115:4–115:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:20\">ISA 40:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:5\">JER 10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:10\">JER 10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:14-Jer10:15\">JER 10:14–10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:17-Jer51:18\">JER 51:17–51:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:18\">HAB 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:5\">MAT 24:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:6\">MRK 13:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:8\">LUK 21:8</a></p>\n<h2>Human wisdom is unreliable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:19-1Cor3:20\">1CO 3:19–3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:36\">JDG 20:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:13\">JOB 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:12-Isa30:13\">ISA 30:12–30:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:4\">ISA 59:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:6-Ezek28:7\">EZK 28:6–28:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:22\">ROM 1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:19-1Cor1:21\">1CO 1:19–1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:25\">1CO 1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:23\">COL 2:23</a></p>\n<h2>Military strength is unreliable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:6\">PSA 44:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:45\">1SA 17:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:16-Ps33:17\">PSA 33:16–33:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:1\">ISA 31:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:4-Isa36:6\">ISA 36:4–36:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:26\">EZK 33:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos1:7\">HOS 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:22\">HAG 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:52\">MAT 26:52</a></p>\n<h2>Material wealth is unreliable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">PRO 11:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:10\">PSA 62:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:4\">JER 49:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:9\">HAG 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:16-Hag2:17\">HAG 2:16–2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:3-Zech9:4\">ZEC 9:3–9:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19\">MAT 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:22\">MAT 13:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:19\">MRK 4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:14\">LUK 8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9-1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:9–6:10</a></p>\n<h2>The consequences of unreliability</h2>\n<h3>Unreliable actions let God down</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:2-Hos11:3\">HOS 11:2–11:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:7\">ISA 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:21\">JER 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:34\">MAT 26:34</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:30\">MRK 14:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:34\">LUK 22:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:10-Luke16:12\">LUK 16:10–16:12</a></p>\n<h3>Unreliability leads to disappointment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:7-Jas1:8\">JAS 1:7–1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:30\">MAT 21:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:43\">MAT 21:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:10-Luke16:12\">LUK 16:10–16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:37-Acts15:38\">ACT 15:37–15:38</a></p>\n<h2>Trust in unreliable things</h2>\n<h3>Leads to self-delusion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:20\">ISA 44:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:10\">ISA 47:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:20\">LUK 12:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17\">REV 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>Leads to judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:5\">JER 17:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:13-Ps49:14\">PSA 49:13–49:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:5-Ps52:7\">PSA 52:5–52:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa20:5\">ISA 20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:25\">JER 46:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:1\">AMO 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:7\">AMO 6:7</a></p>\n<h2>Unreliable people are judged</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:9\">EZK 13:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa20:6\">ISA 20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:7-Mal2:9\">MAL 2:7–2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:38\">MAT 23:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:26-Matt25:27\">MAT 25:26–25:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:22-Luke19:23\">LUK 19:22–19:23</a></p>\n<h2>God is never unreliable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num23:19\">NUM 23:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1KI 8:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:6\">PSA 71:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:26\">JHN 8:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:20\">2CO 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:2\">TIT 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:18\">HEB 6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:13-1John4:16\">1JN 4:13–4:16</a></p>",
